getAttributes

public AttributeList getAttributes(Context context)
                            throws MatrixException
Get a list of all non-hidden attributes for this Relationship. This interface populates the _hasChoices and _choices data members for attributes with range values, which can be expensive for attributes that have lengthy lists of range values or program range values. If _hasChoices and _choices are not needed, use the more efficient getAttributeValues methods.
Parameters:
context - the context for this request
Returns:
the list of Attributes of this Relationship
Throws:
MatrixException - when unable to retrieve data from the BOS
Since:
ADK 6.0

getAttributeValues

public AttributeList getAttributeValues(Context context,
                                        StringList attributeNames)
                                 throws MatrixException
Get the non-hidden Attributes of a Relationship given a list of attribute names. This sets the _attributeType, _value, and _isMultiLine data members of the returned attributes. It does NOT set _hasChoices and _choices If _hasChoices or _choices are needed, use the getAttributes interface.
Parameters:
context - the context for this request.
attributeNames - a StringList of the object attributes to return.
Returns:
the AttributeList for this Relationship.
Throws:
MatrixException - when unable to retrieve data.
Since:
ADK 9.1.0

getAttributeValues

public AttributeList getAttributeValues(Context context,
                                        StringList attributeNames,
                                        boolean getHidden)
                                 throws MatrixException
Get the Attributes of a Relationship, with hidden/non-hidden option, given a list of attribute names. This sets the _attributeType, _value, and _isMultiLine data members of the returned attributes. It does NOT set _hasChoices and _choices If _hasChoices or _choices are needed, use the getAttributes interface.
Parameters:
context - the context for this request.
attributeNames - a StringList of the object attributes to return.
getHidden - if true, return all attributes; if false, return only non-hidden attributes
Returns:
the AttributeList for this Relationship.
Throws:
MatrixException - when unable to retrieve data.
